title: The Man from Utah 1934 (Western Movie) John Wayne, Polly Ann Young, Anita Campillo

sources.title: The Man from Utah 1934 (Western Movie) John Wayne, Polly Ann Young, Anita Campillo
sources.description:
Action on the Range and in the Rodeo!
In a horse-riding rodeo contest bad guys want John Weston to lose. When he doesn't go along they add some insurance: a poisoned needle just under his saddle.

Colorized version: https://youtu.be/Fq2Cwdp951s


Original title: The Man from Utah (1934) AKA: Rodeo
This film is available with English & Spanish audio, and also subtitles in many languages.

Director: Robert N. Bradbury
Writers: Lindsley Parsons, Lindsley Parsons
Stars: John Wayne, Polly Ann Young, Anita Campillo & George 'Gabby' Hayes
Genre: Western, Drama, Classic cinema.


00:00 Full Movie (with subtitles)
03:20 Undercover deputy teams up with a cowboy to investigate suspicious activities at a Rodeo event.
16:33 A stranger named Weston helps the Carters in Dalton, leading to suspicions about the rodeo gang.
18:29 Rodeo organizer seeks help to keep event honest, offers deputy sheriff role to main character.
27:40 Cowboy encounters rodeo committee head and discusses past incidents and future plans.
32:55 A man named Weston is recruited by a gang to participate in a betting scheme at a rodeo event.
36:16 High-stakes rodeo competition with a plot to sabotage the leading contestant's performance.
43:53 Undercover marshal exposes rodeo gang's criminal activities in Utah town.
